The Napkin
===========================================

This is a quick sketch program that is meant for use with a wacom tablet.

It is an experiment in Bug-Driven Development.  It's an experiment in reactive programming.

Bugs
-------------------------------------------

Bug00001 - The app wont start
Bug00002 - Moving the stylus over the napkin doesn't make a mark
Bug00003 - The Stylus doesn't vary with pressure
Bug00004 - The pressure lines arent' smooth